    \u0111\u1ED5i th\xE0nh qu\xE1i v\u1EADt. \u0110\u1EEBng l\u1EA1i g\u1EA7n n\u1EBFu
    kh\xF4ng s\u1EB5n s\xE0ng. Ti\xEAu di\u1EC7t c\xF4 ta \u0111\u1EC3 qua h\xE0nh
    lang."
